---
---
<section id="quality" class="py-16 bg-slate-900 text-white blueprint-grid-dark border-b-8 border-brand-blue">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Technology & Digital Infrastructure -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex flex-col justify-between space-y-6">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-4">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-8 bg-accent block"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-condensed font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">TECHNOLOGY PLATFORM</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
            Powered by Tekla Structures
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-350 leading-relaxed font-sans mb-6">
            Our structural steel drafting workflow is built around Tekla Structures, the global gold standard for structural steel BIM modeling. This enables us to maintain absolute geometric accuracy, run automated clash checks, and export error-free shop files directly.
          </p>

          <!-- 4 Tech highlights -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <!-- Item 1 -->
            <div class="bg-brand-blue/30 border border-slate-800 p-4 rounded-none">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">Robust Model Capacity</h3>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-1">Scale project teams immediately to meet tight fabricator schedules without modeling bottlenecks.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Item 2 -->
            <div class="bg-brand-blue/30 border border-slate-800 p-4 rounded-none">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">Secure Cloud Storage</h3>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-1">Structured file-sharing using secure OneDrive folders ensuring fast, transparent drawing access.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Item 3 -->
            <div class="bg-brand-blue/30 border border-slate-800 p-4 rounded-none">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">Power Redundancy</h3>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-1">Our offices operate with redundant battery backups and generators to ensure uninterrupted support.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Item 4 -->
            <div class="bg-brand-blue/30 border border-slate-800 p-4 rounded-none">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">Redundant Data Backups</h3>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-1">Daily project revisions are backed up offsite to guarantee zero risk of data loss.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Structured Multi-Stage QA System -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
        <div class="bg-white text-slate-850 p-8 border-t-4 border-accent rounded-none">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
            <!-- Shield icon -->
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-navy">
              Quality Assurance Checking Workflow
            </h3>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mb-6">
            Quality is systematically built into our detailing process at every design stage, not just checked at the end. We aim to minimize RFIs and deliver fabrication-ready files on day one.
          </p>

          <!-- Checklists Stages -->
          <div class="space-y-4">
            
            <!-- Stage 1 -->
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-brand-navy text-white font-condensed font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">1</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-brand-navy">Model-Level Clash Checks</h4>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-0.5">Automated Tekla collision reviews checking bolt alignments, beam-column fittings, and erection clearances.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 2 -->
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-brand-navy text-white font-condensed font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">2</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-brand-navy">Dedicated Checker Audit</h4>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-0.5">Experienced senior checkers compare extracted drawings line-by-line against engineer design schemes.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 3 -->
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-brand-navy text-white font-condensed font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">3</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-brand-navy">Australian Standards Verification</h4>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-0.5">Verification of weld sizes (AS 1554), steel grades (AS 4100), and drafting conventions (AS 1100).</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 4 -->
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-brand-navy text-white font-condensed font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">4</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-brand-navy">Pre-Issue Package Validation</h4>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-0.5">Final validation of CNC NC1 data, weight summaries, assembly lists, and drawing scales before distribution.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
